OL,3,CFather who murdered daughter will not
OL,4,Chave sentence increased
OL,6,FJudges at the Court of Appeal have
OL,7,Fruled that a father who murdered his
OL,8,Fdaughter at their home will not have
OL,9,Fhis sentence increased.
OL,11,FSimon Vickers, 50, stabbed his 14-year-
OL,12,Fold daughter Scarlett Vickers through
OL,13,Fthe heart on 5 July 2024, at their
OL,14,Fhome in Darlington.
OL,16,FHe was given a life sentence with a
OL,17,Fminimum of 15 years in jail - the
OL,18,Flowest sentence possible for murder.
