OL,3,CFather who murdered daughter will not
OL,4,Chave sentence increased
OL,6,FAn appeal was submitted to the
OL,7,FAttorney General, which argued that
OL,8,Fthe sentence was unduly lenient.
OL,10,FToday (Thursday 15 May), Court of
OL,11,FAppeal judges ruled the sentence
OL,12,Fshould remain the same.
OL,14,FVickers, of Geneva Road, denied
OL,15,FScarlett's murder all through his
OL,16,Ftrial at Teesside Crown Court.
