OL,3,CFather who murdered daughter will not
OL,4,Chave sentence increased
OL,6,FHe described what happened as a "freak
OL,7,Faccident" in a kitchen "play fight".
OL,8,FThe prosecution said that the 11cm
OL,9,Fwound in Scarlett's chest was too deep
OL,10,Fto have been caused accidentally.
OL,12,FA jury did not believe his testimony
OL,13,Fand found him guilty of Scarlett's
OL,14,Fmurder on Monday 27 January.
OL,16,FScarlett was the only child of Vickers
OL,17,Fand his partner Sarah Hall, who has
OL,18,Fsince stood by him.
