OL,6,FMs Hall, who said she been cooking
OL,7,Fspaghetti bolognese in the kitchen
OL,8,Fwith them that night, has been with
OL,9,FVickers for 27 years.
OL,11,FShe said in court that he would "never
OL,12,Fhurt her," and since the jury's
OL,13,Fverdict, has maintained that she
OL,14,Fbelieves her partner would have never
OL,15,Fhurt Scarlett deliberately.
